mainText:
I dont know why I feel such a pain in my heart, I never met you.&nbsp; But I have been buying your products since before they were "cool".&nbsp; I've stuck by my mac for the last 15 years and I still listen to my boxy 2nd gen iPod.&nbsp; 


Your brilliance and innovation has forever changed us.&nbsp; I watched Apple grow over the last few years and thought, I knew they were special.

Its because of you Mr. Jobs.&nbsp; You will forever be missed.
